info.name: Kids Meal - Veg
info.description: Our Kids' Meal Burger is perfect for little appetites! Golden Mix Vegetable patty served on a soft, freshly baked bun. Topped with a slice of melted cheese slice,crisp lettuce, Tomato ketchup, Creamy Mayonnaise and a slice of red Onion it's a delightful and wholesome treat. Comes with a side of golden, crispy fries and a choice of a small drink Crayons Color nd Hand made Chocolate .Fun, tasty, and made just for kids!
